</p>

<h3><strong>GET</strong> <code>/api/users/</code> ðŸ”’</h3>
<p>Returns the current authenticated user, without its password</p>

<h3><strong>GET</strong> <code>/api/users/{id}</code></h3>
<p>Returns a user with a matching <code>id</code>, without its password</p>

<h3><strong>GET</strong> <code>/api/users/contacts/</code> ðŸ”’</h3>
<p>Returns a list of all the users the user has a conversation with</p>

<h3><strong>GET</strong> <code>/api/users/byEmail/{email}</code></h3>
<p>Returns a user with a matching <code>email</code>, without its password</p>

<h3><strong>GET</strong> <code>/api/users/search/?email={email}</code></h3>
<p>Returns a list of users with a matching <code>email</code>, without their passwords</p>

<h3><strong>PUT</strong> <code>/api/users/</code> ðŸ”’</h3>
<p>Updates the authenticated user's info (not including its password)</p>
<h4>Request body</h4>
<ul>
	<li><strong>username (optional)</strong></li>
	<li><strong>email (optional)</strong></li>
	<li><strong>profilePicture (optional)</strong></li>
</ul>

<h3><strong>DELETE</strong> <code>/api/users/</code> ðŸ”’</h3>
<p>Deletes the authenticated user</p>

